{"tid":2415431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉拒掃安心出行及襲擊餐廳職員 警方：男子疑有精神病","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:55:57.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce283a2abe6772bc7adc6fbe1c18c921cfdeea1e","tid":2415431,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"涉拒掃安心出行及襲擊餐廳職員 男子疑有精神病<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名21歲男子，他涉嫌日前在彩雲邨一間連鎖快餐店拒絕掃瞄「安心出行」二維碼，並涉嫌襲擊店內職員。<br />\n<br />\n事發在星期四清晨6時45分，涉事男子前往彩雲邨商場一間連鎖快餐店購買食品，懷疑不滿要事先以手機掃瞄「安心出行」二維碼，與店員發生言語爭執，有人將手中的手提電話投擲向店員，之後逃去，店員眼角受傷，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日傍晚拘捕涉事男子，在他住所檢獲衣物及手機，男子保釋候查。警方懷疑男子有精神病，所使用的智能手機，並無安裝「安心出行」程式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576575-20210220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576575-20210220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=1e6696b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576575-20210220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=87753f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576575-20210220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3e2eb497637c0b7088b2ae3306d1e358d081508e","tid":2415431,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"撚廚仔d friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e95eed856501d7086f499faa2759c883b263e8","tid":2415431,"uid":108359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"有精神病都清醒過180萬人"},{"pid":"c26e0684161ad6c98c2d9ddff1f1757193d8fc29","tid":2415431,"uid